https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uIhO3e2ZET07DANzIc7RBuOhDyx.jpg Catherine Deneuve couldn’t care less about being a celebrity, but fame made her an icon long ago and she occupies a special place in our imagination. The star is not one to let others get too close, but when she gives you her confidence, she keeps her word. If Deneuve’s career covers a half-century of cinema, it also bears witness to the force of a generation that experienced the deepest transformation of mores. This portrait reflects her entirely. The story of a mystery and an adventure. Catherine Deneuve, belle et bien là
